# RECALL TOUCH — DEFINITIVE CURSOR MASTER PROMPT
# Paste as .cursorrules. Read ALL before writing ANY code. Implement code — ship each wave.

CONTEXT: Recall Touch (recall-touch.com). Next.js + Tailwind + Supabase. Do NOT depend on Supabase for public pages.
GOAL: Premium product feel — not template, not AI-slop.

RULES: TypeScript. Public page.tsx = Server Component (no "use client", no useEffect, no supabase). Interactive = "use client" islands + mount guard + skeleton. Browser-only = dynamic(..., { ssr: false }). Auth in middleware only /app/*. Forms: localStorage first → API (catch silent) → success. npm run build after every file. No "Verifying session" / blank / spinner.

STEP A — REPO RECON: Run build, lint, fix all errors before proceeding.

STEP B — VERIFIED BUGS (fix all): 1) Signup dead end — one button "Set up my AI agent →" only. 2) No false email promise. 3) Sign-in via localStorage match. 4) /demo plays. 5) Homepage preview has call cards. 6) Pricing toggle works. 7) Waitlist saves. 8) All pages exist. 9) /app shell + onboarding + activity. 10) sitemap + robots. 11) Styled error/404. 12) Activate has NavBar. 13) Tab title Recall Touch. 14) Success screen = one CTA, no competing links.

STEP C — BRAND: "AI answers your business calls 24/7 so you never miss a lead." SMB owner. Confident, Clean, Capable. Dark theme.

STEP D — DESIGN: bg-black, bg-zinc-950 sidebar, bg-zinc-900/50 cards, text-white headings, text-zinc-400 body. Primary btn: bg-white text-black rounded-xl. NavBar: Logo | Product, Pricing, Demo, Docs | Sign in, Start free →. Footer: 4 cols + "AI phone system for every business".

WAVE 1 — UNBREAK MONEY PATH: Root layout Server Component, html class dark, body bg-black. /activate: NavBar, success = "Welcome aboard!" + one button + "Takes 2 minutes · Your first 14 days are free". /app shell (client, mount guard), banner "Demo Mode — Forward your number [Set up →]", redirect !rt_onboarded → onboarding. /app/onboarding 5 steps. /app/activity 4 stats, filters, 5 demo cards, milestone. Homepage preview animated cards (ssr:false). Pricing toggle. Waitlist. middleware + error.tsx + not-found.tsx.

WAVE 2 — PUBLIC PAGES: /demo CallSimulator 3 tabs. /product 8 sections. /pricing toggle+calculator+FAQ. /sign-in. /docs. /contact, /privacy, /terms. /blog + 3. /industries/[slug]. API routes. SEO.

WAVE 3 — APP + ANTI-CHURN: contacts, agents, campaigns, messages, calendar, analytics, settings (8 sub). Cancel flow. Milestones, inactivity banner, onboarding checklist, ROI card, toasts.

WAVE 4 — POLISH: Mobile 375px, motion, a11y, performance, final QA.

VERIFICATION: Core flow works. All pages render. No Verifying session, no dead buttons, no 404 on linked routes. build + lint pass.
